name: Object#002
description:
Another strange ASCII object. It's shape changes according to a variable X which can take on values between 0.05 and 0.45. Observe and find out what it is like!
Controls: 
- set the value of variable X manually or toggle it's animation using the ui in the upper right corner
- control the camera rotation by dragging 
- control the camera zoom by mousewheel or pinch
